---AD.1.7.98 Identify and Authenticate Users
"Session timeout	15 minutes

"TMOUT environment variable in /etc/profile

egrep 'TMOUT=|[[:space:]][[:space:]]*TMOUT[[:space:]]|[[:space:]][[:space:]]*TMOUT$' /etc/profile /etc/profile.d/*

"*/
"Si no esta en /etc/profile o /etc/profile.d/*, se puede buscar en otro lugar:

grep TMOUT $HOME/.??* /etc/* 2> /dev/null

"*/
" CONTESTAR YES*/ 
"si retorna:
export TMOUT=$X
or
TMOUT=$X
"	- para servidores PCI, sustituya $X por 15 m, or  900 s

" CONTESTAR NO   TMOUT is not configured, recommended at 15 minutes or 900 seconds.


